long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1262582 Settings option
Description of problem: On qbittorrent the options are not visible
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
How reproducible: Install Fedora 25, install qbittorrent
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Go to qbittorrent options page, under connections settings see the setting "Port used..." 2. 3.
Actual results: The textbox is not visible
Expected results:
Additional info:
The same issue is also experienced in VLC. Advanced preferences parameters text box are also not visible.
Thanks for the report. This seems like a valid problem of the theme.

Hmm, I have no idea at all how to fix this properly. It seems Qt doesn't care about the size the spinbox has reported. I'm now just checking there's enough space and if not, the control buttons will be shrinked. I'll push the update in a while.
